<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Support Ticket Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .ticket-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Support Ticket Created</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>User Email: <strong><%= userEmail %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for contacting our support team. Your ticket has been successfully created and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        
        <div class="ticket-details">
            <h2>Ticket Details</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> <%= ticketId %></li>
                <li><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= ticketSubject %></li>
                <li><strong>Created At:</strong> <%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleString() %></li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Your Message</h3>
            <p><%= ticketDescription %></p>
        </div>

        <p>Our support team will review your request and respond within 24-48 hours. You'll receive another email when we update your ticket.</p>
        
        <p>If you need to add any additional information, please reply to this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>Support Team</strong></p>
        <p><%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Â© Your Company Name</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>